---
// src/components/CTA.astro
---

<section
    class="pt-56 pb-60 py-40 px-6 lg:px-12 bg-[var(--rosa-pale)] text-[var(--verde)] relative overflow-hidden"
    id="cta"
>
    <div
        class="absolute inset-0 bg-[var(--rosa-pale)]"
    >
    </div>
    <div
        class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-full h-full bg-[radial-gradient(circle,rgba(232,68,122,0.12)_0%,transparent_70%)] pointer-events-none"
    >
    </div>
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center relative z-10">
        <span
            class="text-[var(--verde-mid)] text-xs font-extrabold uppercase tracking-[0.4em] mb-10 block"
            >¿Listo para dar el paso?</span
        >
        <h2
            class="serif text-5xl lg:text-7xl mt-8 mb-10 leading-[0.9] tracking-tight"
        >
            Transforma la gestión <em>DUAL</em> de tu centro hoy.
        </h2>
        <p
            class="text-[var(--verde)]/70 text-xl mb-16 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed"
        >
            Pide una demostración gratuita y descubre por qué más del 50% de los centros públicos de FP del País Vasco ya confían en dual365.
        </p>
        <div class="max-w-xl mx-auto">
            <form class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-4 mb-8">
                <input
                    class="flex-1 bg-white/60 border border-[var(--verde)]/100 rounded-full px-8 py-5 focus:outline-none focus:border-[var(--verde)] transition-colors placeholder:text-[var(--verde)]/40 text-[var(--verde)]"
                    placeholder="Email del centro"
                    type="email"
                />
                <button
                    class="bg-[var(--verde)] text-white font-extrabold px-8 py-5 rounded-full shadow-2xl shadow-emerald-500/25 hover:scale-105 transition-transform flex items-center justify-center gap-2"
                    type="button"
                >
                    Solicitar Demo <span
                        class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm"
                        >rocket_launch</span
                    >
                </button>
            </form>
            <div
                class="flex items-center justify-center gap-6 text-[var(--verde)]/50 text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest"
            >
                <span>✓ Respuesta &lt; 24h</span>
                <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-[var(--verde)]/20 rounded-full"></span>
                <span>✓ Demo Personalizada</span>
                <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-[var(--verde)]/20 rounded-full"></span>
                <span>✓ Sin Compromiso</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
